body text-[13.5px] font-medium text-ink group-hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150\">Gestion Immobilière</span><span class=\"font-body text-xs text-muted mt-0.5 leading-relaxed\">Gestion locative, suivi financier et accompagnement juridique.</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[180px]\"><div><p class=\"font-display text-[17px] font-semibold text-navy mb-2.5 leading-snug\">Tous nos services</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed\">Un accompagnement complet pour chaque dimension de votre entreprise.</p></div><a class=\"mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-body text-[13px] font-semibold text-gold hover:gap-2.5 transition-all duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded\" href=\"/fr/services\">Voir les services<svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div></div></div><div id=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden absolute left-0 right-0 top-full bg-white border-t border-black/[0.06] transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0 pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><nav aria-label=\"Navigation mobile\"><ul class=\"container-main pt-3 pb-6 flex flex-col\"><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr\">Accueil</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-3 px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium text-ink transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded\">Services<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 text-muted/50 rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polyline points=\"9 18 15 12 9 6\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-3 space-y-4\"><div><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold text-muted tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 px-1\">Finances &amp; Fiscalité</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col\"><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/comptabilite-fiscalite\">Comptabilité &amp; Fiscalité</a></li><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/ressources-humaines\">Ressources Humaines</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] font-semibold text-muted tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-1.5 px-1\">Administration &amp; Immobilier</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col\"><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-administrative\">Gestion administrative</a></li><li><a class=\"block px-3 py-2.5 font-body text-sm text-ink hover:text-gold transition-colors duration-150 rounded focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold\" href=\"/fr/services/gestion-immobiliere\">Gestion Immobilière</a></li></ul></div></div></div></li><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-gold\" aria-current=\"page\" href=\"/fr/qui-sommes-nous\">Qui sommes-nous</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-black/[0.05] last:border-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center px-1 py-3.5 font-body text-sm font-medium rounded transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold text-ink hover:text-gold\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4 mt-3 pt-4 border-t border-black/[0.06] px-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Language selector\"><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-gold\" aria-pressed=\"true\">FR</button><span class=\"mx-1 text-[11px] text-black/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\">|</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-ink/35 hover:text-ink\" aria-pressed=\"false\">EN</button><span class=\"mx-1 text-[11px] text-black/15\" aria-hidden=\"true\">|</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"font-body text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wider transition-colors duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold rounded px-0.5 text-ink/35 hover:text-ink\" aria-pressed=\"false\">PT</button></span></div><a class=\"btn-primary text-xs py-2 px-4\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Demander une offre</a></li></ul></nav></div></header><main><section class=\"relative bg-navy overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-20 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-24\"><div class=\"hero-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.025]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"absolute -top-24 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full border border-gold/8 pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"container-main relative z-10 text-center\"><span class=\"section-label text-gold/70\">Le cabinet</span><h1 class=\"font-display font-light text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.015em] text-white mt-2 mb-6\">Qui<!-- --> <span class=\"italic font-light text-champagne\">sommes-nous</span></h1><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-px bg-gold/40\"></div></div><p class=\"font-body text-white/55 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Fondé par des professionnels romands passionnés, SRD Partners est bien plus qu&#x27;un cabinet fiduciaire : c&#x27;est un partenaire engagé dans la durée.</p></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-cream\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 0,80\" fill=\"#46184E\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><span class=\"section-label\">Notre mission</span><h2 class=\"section-title mb-6\">Accompagner les entrepreneurs avec rigueur</h2><p class=\"font-body text-muted leading-relaxed\">Chez SRD Partners, notre mission est simple : vous permettre de vous concentrer sur votre cœur de métier, pendant que nous veillons à la santé financière, fiscale et administrative de votre entreprise.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-body text-sm font-semibold text-navy hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors mt-8 group\" href=\"/fr/contact\">Prendre rendez-vous<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"></line><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"></polyline></svg></a></div><div class=\"mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-black/[0.07] grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-y-8 sm:gap-y-10 sm:divide-x divide-black/[0.07]\"><div class=\"text-center py-6\"><p class=\"font-display text-[2rem] sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-champagne leading-none mb-2\">0<!-- -->+</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-muted tracking-wide\">Années d&#x27;expérience</p></div><div class=\"text-center py-6\"><p class=\"font-display text-[2rem] sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-champagne leading-none mb-2\">0<!-- -->+</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-muted tracking-wide\">Clients accompagnés</p></div><div class=\"text-center py-6\"><p class=\"font-display text-[2rem] sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-champagne leading-none mb-2\">0</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-muted tracking-wide\">Experts à votre service</p></div><div class=\"text-center py-6\"><p class=\"font-display text-[2rem] sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-champagne leading-none mb-2\">0</p><p class=\"font-body text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-muted tracking-wide\">Bureaux en Romandie</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-stone\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 1440,80\" fill=\"#F8F9FC\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16\"><span class=\"section-label\">Ce qui nous guide</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">Nos valeurs fondamentales</h2></div><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"pb-12 sm:pb-14 last:pb-0\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-semibold text-sm mb-5 select-none\">0<!-- -->1</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-[1.625rem] sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.2]\">Rigueur</h3><p class=\"font-body text-[0.9375rem] text-muted leading-[1.82] max-w-md\">Chaque dossier est traité avec la même exigence. L&#x27;exactitude de nos travaux est non négociable.</p></div><div class=\"pb-12 sm:pb-14 last:pb-0\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-semibold text-sm mb-5 select-none\">0<!-- -->2</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-[1.625rem] sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.2]\">Proximité</h3><p class=\"font-body text-[0.9375rem] text-muted leading-[1.82] max-w-md\">Nous vous connaissons par votre prénom. Vous avez un interlocuteur dédié, disponible et réactif.</p></div><div class=\"pb-12 sm:pb-14 last:pb-0\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-semibold text-sm mb-5 select-none\">0<!-- -->3</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-[1.625rem] sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.2]\">Indépendance</h3><p class=\"font-body text-[0.9375rem] text-muted leading-[1.82] max-w-md\">Nos conseils sont objectifs et formulés dans votre seul intérêt, sans conflit d&#x27;intérêt.</p></div><div class=\"pb-12 sm:pb-14 last:pb-0\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-body font-semibold text-sm mb-5 select-none\">0<!-- -->4</div><h3 class=\"font-display text-[1.625rem] sm:text-3xl font-light text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.2]\">Durabilité</h3><p class=\"font-body text-[0.9375rem] text-muted leading-[1.82] max-w-md\">Nous construisons des relations à long terme, fondées sur la confiance et la transparence.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-mineral\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 0,80\" fill=\"#D2C9D6\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span class=\"section-label\">Notre équipe</span><h2 class=\"section-title\">Des experts à votre écoute</h2><p class=\"section-subtitle mx-auto text-center mt-4\">Des professionnels aguerris, engagés dans leur métier et dans la relation client.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"animate-fade-up delay-100\"><div><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 text-primary-500 flex items-center justify-center font-display text-2xl font-light mb-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\">CH</div><h3 class=\"font-body text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-1\">Cremilde Hirschi</h3><p class=\"font-body text-xs text-gold font-medium tracking-wide mb-4\">Administration · Finance · RH</p><p class=\"font-body text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5\">Interlocutrice principale du cabinet, Cremilde coordonne l&#x27;ensemble des dossiers clients avec rigueur et disponibilité.</p><blockquote class=\"border-l-2 border-gold/40 pl-4\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[0.875rem] text-muted/80 leading-relaxed\">“<!-- -->Je m&#x27;engage personnellement à accompagner chaque client avec rigueur et une totale disponibilité.<!-- -->”</p></blockquote></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"contact\" class=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-stone\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 80\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"height:var(--slant-h)\"><polygon points=\"0,0 1440,0 1440,80\" fill=\"#D2C9D6\"></polygon></svg><div class=\"relative z-10 container-main pt-32 sm:pt-40 pb-28 sm:pb-36\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\"